<div id="stitle" style="display:none;">Letter</div>
<div class="nbunit" id="22Nov1917"><font color="red">22 November 1917</font>, <cite>Pound Letters</cite> (Ezra Pound to LR): I have just written J.Q. that I have a guarantor for &pound;10 for three years &hellip; Mary Sinclair &hellip; It will enable me to pay Joyce the proper &pound;50 for the American rights on his novel. Which is a comfort.</div>
